README.md

Awesome

   A curated list of awesome
   [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Telecommuting]remote working resources.

   To contribute, click README.md and then the pencil icon. Make your
   changes and click the "Propose file change" button to submit a pull
   request. Make sure to follow
   [file://localhost/lukasz-madon/awesome-remote-job/blob/master/CONTRIBUT
   ING.md]the contributions guidelines.

